data.description: SELLER EXTREMELY MOTIVATED! The lanai and garden area on this 4 bedroom 3 bath is extraordinary.  The triple split floor plan,  3 car garage, upstairs bonus and conservation lot make this home a must see . The back of the home opens up to the  outdoor gas kitchen and garden oasis to make entertaining or relaxing pleasurable. The gourmet kitchen with center island has 42" cabinets, new stainless steel appliances and over 14K worth of new quartz countertops. Kitchen is spacious enough for a small dinette and the island adds tons of work or eating space. Kitchen overlooks the family room which opens up to the lanai, perfect for family gatherings and entertaining. The triple split floor plan offers 2 generously sized  bedrooms that share a bathroom.  The rear of the home features a private bedroom and a bathroom, perfect for in-laws or guests. The luxury primary suite is on the other side of the home for complete privacy.  It opens up to the lanai for a peaceful evening gazing at the beautiful garden. The second floor bonus room is set up for a sports lover and all items convey (with the exception of signed memorabilia  on the walls).The carpet has been replaced in the primary bedroom.  Never be bothered by backyard neighbors as your yard is on a conservation lot and set up for relaxation.   A-rated schools; resort style living; fitness centers; tennis/basketball courts, clubhouses, community pools, parks, 28+ miles of running trails, & a sports complex. A Military friendly community that has public transportation to MacDill AFB.
